  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2122180/extras/410c617860077490a29bac216e924828.avif?t=1744799798\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2122180/extras_big/410c617860077490a29bac216e924828.avif?t=1744799798 width=800 height=271 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >OrbHand is a card management game where you help a wizard build his magical tower and defeat the demons, while building a beautiful village in the process. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2122180/extras/0f6aee683da2de353815d022d6a9520d.poster.avif?t=1744799798\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2122180/extras/0f6aee683da2de353815d022d6a9520d.webm?t=1744799798\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2122180/extras/0f6aee683da2de353815d022d6a9520d.mp4?t=1744799798\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game begins with a Wizard card and an Orb card. Make the Wizard ponder the Orb and start generating Mana, the most basic resource in the game. You will use it to purchase booster packs, to make new buildings and resources and to create spells.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Stack</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stack your cards to create new buildings, and assign resource cards to them to create more powerful characters and spells. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Make new allies</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Recruit new characters to help you produce resources, fight enemies and cast spells. Each one has it's own unique capabilities! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Cast spells and fight enemies</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2122180/extras/fd8c98e75d52cfc5888e1e7b6bfd2e66.poster.avif?t=1744799798\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2122180/extras/fd8c98e75d52cfc5888e1e7b6bfd2e66.webm?t=1744799798\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2122180/extras/fd8c98e75d52cfc5888e1e7b6bfd2e66.mp4?t=1744799798\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Produce and cast spell cards that can greatly impact the gameboard.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight goblins, elves and other creatures that invade your town. Defeat five bosses and survive the last encounter against the Demon hordes.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Characteristics</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 🃏 Drag and drop cards to stack and assign them 🃏</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 🧙‍♂️ Make allies and fight evil cards 🧙‍♂️</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- ⚡ Create and cast spells ⚡</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 🏛️ Make new buildings 🏛️</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 🔎 Unlock recipes 🔍</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 💰 Complete objectives to receive rewards 💰</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 🏯 Build the Tower 🏯</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 😈 Defeat the Demons! 😈</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2122180/extras/410c617860077490a29bac216e924828.avif?t=1744799798\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2122180/extras_big/410c617860077490a29bac216e924828.avif?t=1744799798 width=800 height=271 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >OrbHand is a card management game where you help a wizard build his magical tower and defeat the demons, while building a beautiful village in the process. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2122180/extras/0f6aee683da2de353815d022d6a9520d.poster.avif?t=1744799798\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2122180/extras/0f6aee683da2de353815d022d6a9520d.webm?t=1744799798\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2122180/extras/0f6aee683da2de353815d022d6a9520d.mp4?t=1744799798\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game begins with a Wizard card and an Orb card. Make the Wizard ponder the Orb and start generating Mana, the most basic resource in the game. You will use it to purchase booster packs, to make new buildings and resources and to create spells.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Stack</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stack your cards to create new buildings, and assign resource cards to them to create more powerful characters and spells. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Make new allies</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Recruit new characters to help you produce resources, fight enemies and cast spells. Each one has it's own unique capabilities! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Cast spells and fight enemies</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2122180/extras/fd8c98e75d52cfc5888e1e7b6bfd2e66.poster.avif?t=1744799798\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2122180/extras/fd8c98e75d52cfc5888e1e7b6bfd2e66.webm?t=1744799798\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2122180/extras/fd8c98e75d52cfc5888e1e7b6bfd2e66.mp4?t=1744799798\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Produce and cast spell cards that can greatly impact the gameboard.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight goblins, elves and other creatures that invade your town. Defeat five bosses and survive the last encounter against the Demon hordes.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Characteristics</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 🃏 Drag and drop cards to stack and assign them 🃏</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 🧙‍♂️ Make allies and fight evil cards 🧙‍♂️</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- ⚡ Create and cast spells ⚡</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 🏛️ Make new buildings 🏛️</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 🔎 Unlock recipes 🔍</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 💰 Complete objectives to receive rewards 💰</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 🏯 Build the Tower 🏯</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 😈 Defeat the Demons! 😈</p>",
